# AI Prompt 管理器 - 项目架构图

## 1. 整体架构图

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph 前端层["前端层 (React 18)"]
        App[App.tsx<br>根组件]
        Router[React Router<br>路由管理]

        subgraph Pages["页面组件"]
            Login[LoginPage<br>登录页]
            Dashboard[DashboardPage<br>仪表盘]
            PromptList[PromptListPage<br>Prompt列表]
            PromptDetail[PromptDetailPage<br>Prompt详情]
            Settings[SettingsPage<br>设置页]
        end

        subgraph Contexts["状态管理"]
            AuthCtx[AuthContext<br>认证状态]
            PromptCtx[PromptContext<br>Prompt状态]
        end

        subgraph Lib["工具库"]
            Supabase[supabase.ts<br>Supabase客户端]
        end
    end

    subgraph 后端层["后端层 (Supabase)"]
        Auth[Supabase Auth<br>用户认证]
        DB[(PostgreSQL<br>数据库)]

        subgraph Tables["数据表"]
            Profiles[profiles<br>用户表]
            Categories[categories<br>分类表]
            Prompts[prompts<br>Prompt表]
        end
    end

    App --> Router
    Router --> Pages
    Pages --> Contexts
    Contexts --> Lib
    Lib --> Supabase
    Supabase --> Auth
    Supabase --> DB
    Auth --> DB
```

---

## 2. 组件结构图

```mermaid
graph TB
    App --> AuthProvider
    App --> PromptProvider
    App --> BrowserRouter

    BrowserRouter --> Routes
    Routes --> Route1["/login → LoginPage"]
    Routes --> Route2["/ → DashboardPage"]
    Routes --> Route3["/prompts → PromptListPage"]
    Routes --> Route4["/prompts/:id → PromptDetailPage"]
    Routes --> Route5["/settings → SettingsPage"]

    AuthProvider --> AuthCtx
    PromptProvider --> PromptCtx

    AuthCtx --> supabase
    PromptCtx --> supabase

    supabase -.-> Auth
    supabase -.-> DB
```

