## 3. 数据库模型图

```mermaid
erDiagram
    profiles {
        uuid id PK
        timestamp created_at
    }

    categories {
        uuid id PK
        uuid user_id FK
        text name
        uuid parent_id FK
        integer sort_order
        timestamp created_at
    }

    prompts {
        uuid id PK
        uuid user_id FK
        text title
        text content
        uuid category_id FK
        text[] tags
        jsonb variables
        integer usage_count
        timestamp created_at
        timestamp updated_at
    }

    profiles ||--o{ categories : "用户拥有"
    profiles ||--o{ prompts : "用户创建"
    categories ||--o{ categories : "自关联"
    categories ||--o{ prompts : "包含"
```

