## 5. 状态管理架构

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph AuthContext["AuthContext"]
        A1["user: User | null"]
        A2["loading: boolean"]
        A3["login()"]
        A4["logout()"]
        A5["register()"]
    end

    subgraph PromptContext["PromptContext"]
        P1["prompts: Prompt[]"]
        P2["categories: Category[]"]
        P3["tags: string[]"]
        P4["selectedPrompt: Prompt | null"]
        P5["fetchPrompts()"]
        P6["createPrompt()"]
        P7["updatePrompt()"]
        P8["deletePrompt()"]
        P9["searchPrompts()"]
    end

    subgraph SupabaseClient["supabase Client"]
        S1["URL配置"]
        S2["Anon Key"]
        S3["createClient()"]
    end

    AuthContext -.-> SupabaseClient
    PromptContext -.-> SupabaseClient
```

